    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You seriously have to see this beauty in person! I have babied this car since day one, and it's honestly in such incredible shape that it still feels brand new. It's been kept in a garage, sparkles inside and out, and drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready to hit the road today, this is the one! Drop me a message if you have any questions\u2014I'd love to tell you more about it!",
