      "description": "Presenting an exceptional specimen maintained to the highest standards of automotive preservation. This vehicle exhibits a pristine aesthetic and mechanical integrity synonymous with showroom delivery. Every surface, from the hand-finished upholstery to the unblemished exterior, reflects a rigorous commitment to maintenance. For the discerning collector or professional requiring uncompromising quality, this remains a peerless acquisition.",
      "price": 48500.0,
