      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, it is a total gem! This car is in stunning, showroom-ready condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the lot. It\u2019s been pampered since day one, always kept in the garage, and drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for perfection on wheels, you've found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come see it in person!",
      "price": 46500.0,
